        <updateDate>2021-02-22T22:00:58Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill extends to November 25, 2025, the period of temporary authority for the Department of Defense (DOD) to extend contracts and leases under the Armament Retooling and Manufacturing Support Program (i.e., ARMS initiative). The authority allows DOD to extend a contract or lease for an additional 25 years. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
